&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This conversation is co-sponsored by the &lt;a href="https://www.sipa.columbia.edu/sipa-education/masters-programs/specializations/technology-media-and-communications"&gt;Technology, Media, and Communications specialization&lt;/a&gt; at Columbia&amp;rsquo;s School of International and Public Affairs and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://worldprojects.columbia.edu/"&gt;Columbia World Projects&lt;/a&gt;. This in-person event is free and open to the public. All those interested in understanding what&amp;rsquo;s at stake for democracy and how journalism can help protect it are encouraged to attend.&lt;/p&gt;
