&lt;p&gt;Join us for an engaging book launch featuring three authors exploring some of today&amp;rsquo;s most pressing issues through their latest works. Sara Gorman, HPM alum, discusses the rise of medical mistrust in &amp;quot;The Anatomy of Deception.&amp;quot; Professor Howard Friedman offers a practical guide to &amp;quot;Winning with Data Science&amp;quot; for business leaders. Professor Mitch Stripling delves into the societal shifts triggered by crises in &amp;quot;The Epistemology of Disasters and Social Change.&amp;quot; The authors will participate in a panel discussion, offering unique perspectives on public health, business, and societal transformation. Don&amp;rsquo;t miss this opportunity for thought-provoking conversation and connection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There will be a reception and book purchase/signing to follow.&lt;/p&gt;
