&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shahryar Shaghaghi&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;, Professor of Professional Practice, Enterprise Risk Management; Technology, Risk Management and Cybersecurity Executive&lt;/p&gt;
