&lt;p&gt;Her dedication to creating equitable AI systems offer profound insights into the evolving landscape of medical informatics.&amp;nbsp;This event is a remarkable opportunity to gain expert knowledge on how AI is shaping the future of healthcare in ethically responsible ways.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
